### Bank Simulator API Tests - Node.js Version
### Make sure the server is running: npm start or node bank-app.js

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/

### Customer Operations

### Get all customers
GET http://localhost:8000/customers/

### Get specific customer
GET http://localhost:8000/customers/1

### Create a new customer
POST http://localhost:8000/customers/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Alice",
  "last_name": "Wilson",
  "email": "alice.wilson@email.com",
  "phone": "555-0104"
}

### Account Operations

### Get customer's accounts
GET http://localhost:8000/customers/1/accounts

### Get account by number (use actual account number from previous response)
GET http://localhost:8000/accounts/ACC0000000001

### Create a new account for customer
POST http://localhost:8000/accounts/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": 1,
  "account_type": "savings",
  "initial_balance": 1000.00
}

### Transaction Operations

### Deposit money
POST http://localhost:8000/transactions/deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_number": "ACC0000000001",
  "amount": 500.00,
  "description": "Initial deposit"
}

### Withdraw money
POST http://localhost:8000/transactions/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_number": "ACC0000000001",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "description": "ATM withdrawal"
}

### Transfer money between accounts
POST http://localhost:8000/transactions/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from_account_number": "ACC0000000001",
  "to_account_number": "ACC0000000002",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "description": "Transfer to savings"
}

### Get account transaction history
GET http://localhost:8000/accounts/ACC0000000001/transactions

### Error Testing

### Try to withdraw more than balance
POST http://localhost:8000/transactions/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_number": "ACC0000000001",
  "amount": 99999.00,
  "description": "Should fail - insufficient funds"
}

### Try to access non-existent account
GET http://localhost:8000/accounts/INVALID123

### Try to deposit negative amount
POST http://localhost:8000/transactions/deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_number": "ACC0000000001",
  "amount": -100.00,
  "description": "Should fail - negative amount"
}
